Building Wgcclassic

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building Wgcclassic-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Wgcclassic.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building wgcclassicd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Wgcclassic.
